com.yworks.yfiles.utils

Interface ICollection<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the collection's elements.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<T>, IEnumerable<T>, Iterable<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IList<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EdgeList, NodeList, ObservableCollection, YList

    public interface ICollection<T>
extends IEnumerable<T>, Collection<T>
    Common interface for Collections that also provide an enumerator. Also contains some default implementations which facilitate handling of Collections.
